author: @jihoonpanda8295
text: Rintik rinai dengan halus jatuh menyapa bumantara malam ini. Ditemani dengan deru angin tenang membawa hawa sejuk kepada insan yang tengah sibuk bergelung dalam selimut, berharap mendapatkan kehangatan dibaliknya. Insan itu adalah aku, salah satu manusia di bumi ini yang dengan segala keberaninya menjatuhkan hatinya ke sosok lelaki manis berasma Huang Renjun. Suaranya selembut kain sutra, hatinya setulus embun pagi, wajahnya tampan bak sang pangeran, senyumannya melebihi cerahnya langit di musim kemarau, kata-kata motivasi sering terucap dari bibir tipis miliknya, membuat siapapun terus terjatuh kedalam pesonanya. Hai Renjun, terima kasih telah hadir dalam hidupku, terima kasih sudah menjadi alasan dan penyelamat bagi banyak insan untuk terus bangkit. Ingatlah bahwa kita â€”renchinâ€” akan selalu menjadi benteng pelindung mu. love you ğŸ’•

author: @LaVita18
text:
I got lost listening to this. 

The tender way the lyrics were whispered that echoed at the back, interplayed ethereally with the press of the piano. Renjun's clear fine voice is akin to a thin ray of sunshine that caresses the earth; it's a gentle presence that encapsulates you. Despite the sad lyrics, there's something rather comforting with the way Renjun delivered Fate.

I love his vocal colour so much, & I'm happy to hear him using a singing technique we rarely get to hear when he's with the dreamies (though we're getting this style of singing more in the Glitch Mode album) - more so, it showcases his versatility as a vocalist.

I look forward to hearing more versatility Renjun in the future. Thank you for the gift, sweetheart... Though you should know, your voice has always been a gift to me.

author: @saraheal1981
text:
Me and many other fans who love Renjun are very happy whenever Renjun has all the solo content and shows off his beautiful voice. We always fully support Renjun and the response is always good. Renjun is 1 of very popular members in NCT, proven by many statistics. That's SM ent should know because his fans still know. 
From March 23, 2021 to April 1, 2022 this period of one year Renjun has solo content and special content owned by Renjun just 2 videos on nct's youtube and every time there is content of Renjun, there is always a problem that causes the release to be delayed all the time. which those problems are caused by the company's poor management. I wonder what standard SM is using to treat Renjun? The number of Renjun's events was chosen to participateâ€‹ in was significantly less than the other members (The event that nct, nct dream members don't have to go together for the whole group)â€‹â€‹ and Renjun has never been included in the main unit that is the title track of the nct2020 and nct2021 albums, the nct show Renjun join in 1 content out of a total of 8 content including Renjun's solo content that half a year only has 1 timeâ€‹, special stage e.g. at the end of 2021 celebrations and awards ceremony Renjun was the only person in nct dream didn't have a special stage and didn't show breakdance. Did you forget that Renjun is the lead dancer and main vocalist? When Renjun has a solo event SM also doesn't promote him e.g. ELLE idol magazine that has been his only solo event for the past 1 year sm doesn't promote on nct's sns and has no behind the scenes video. I think the way SM treats Renjun is against his popularity.
Renjun was a person with many outstanding talents. He can speak Korean and Chinese fluently and his figure, face and personality are very good. Over a period of 5 years I hope SM ent that claim to be the Asia's no.1 entertainment will see the prominence and fully support his talent in every aspect, but I still haven't seen it. I have always expected that Renjun will have a variety of solo events and solo content that is as consistent and diverse. SM should know that Renjun is very precious to the fans. PLEASE TREAT RENJUN BETTER give him the same chance as many other members and SM should treat every artist in your company fairly.

text:
Renjun, sayangku.

Selamat malam, cahaya hati mama.
Kamu tahu tidak? Kamu berhasil mewujudkan slogan kamu. Kamu bilang, 'seseorang yang menerangi dunia.' Iya sayangku, kamu berhasil nak.

Lihat ya, banyak loh orang-orang yang mungkin hari ini adalah hari buruk, hari yang melelahkan. Tapi kamu beri hadiah kecil ini yang bernar-benar membuat mereka tersenyum dan merasa bahagia hari ini. Kamu menyinari mereka yang harinya gelap sayangku.

Renjun hebat sekali.

Kamu harus bangga dengan dirimu ya.
Karena jutaan orang bangga denganmu nak.

Huang Renjun, I LoVe You.
